@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}

<h1 class="display-4 text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>
<div class="container mt-5">
    <p>Your privacy is of utmost importance at Bookstore Management. This privacy policy explains how we collect, use, and safeguard your personal information when using our platform.</p>
    <h2 class="mt-4">1. Information We Gather</h2>
    <p>When you engage with our Bookstore Management system, we collect the following information to enhance our service:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li><strong>Personal Identification Information:</strong> Name, email address, phone number, and billing information when you register or make purchases.</li>
        <li><strong>Transactional Data:</strong> Purchase history, payment details, and shipping information for orders placed through our platform.</li>
        <li><strong>Technical Information:</strong> IP address, browser type, device type, and access times, which help us improve user experience and system performance.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">2. Purpose of Using Your Information</h2>
    <p>Your information is utilized for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul class="list-unstyled">
        <li>To manage your account and provide customer support.</li>
        <li>To process transactions, including orders, payments, and shipping of books.</li>
        <li>To enhance our platform’s functionality and user experience.</li>
        <li>To send you promotional offers, newsletters, and updates relevant to your interests (with your consent).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2 class="mt-4">3. Data Security Measures</h2>
    <p>We implement robust security measures to protect your personal information. All sensitive data is encrypted, and we utilize industry-standard security protocols to prevent unauthorized access, disclosure, or misuse of your information.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>We do not sell or share your personal information with third parties for their own marketing purposes. However, we may share your data with trusted partners who assist us in operating our platform, provided they agree to safeguard your information in accordance with our standards.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">5. Your Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to access, update, or delete your personal information. If you wish to exercise these rights, please contact our support team.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">6. Changes to This Policy</h2>
    <p>We may update this privacy policy periodically to reflect changes in our practices or the law. We will notify you of any significant changes by updating the date of this document.</p>

    <h2 class="mt-4">7. Get in Touch</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns regarding your privacy or this policy, please reach out to us at <a href="mailto:support@bookstoremanagement.com">support@bookstoremanagement.com</a>.</p>

    <p class="text-muted mt-5">Last Updated: September 29, 2024</p>
</div>
